name: Bali Purana Homestay
address: Desa Tenganan, Dauh Tukad, Kec. Manggis, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80871, Indonesia
review 1: If you look for a basic stay away from the hussle this is it. I stayed in a bungalow next to the wonderful village of Tenganan. Every morning Puri and his wife invited me for a big, delicious and local breakfast. I stayed a week and was submerged in local customs and culture. Nice place to have long walks and there are two hikes nearby. Next to the bungalow there is free wifi.
